## 11. Security / maintenance notes

```powershell
npm audit
npm outdated
```

- Do **not** blindly `npm audit fix --force` if it proposes **downgrading** Angular 21 tooling to 20.
- **`msw` 2.x** is a major upgrade from 1.x — plan separately.

